 on top of cream soda. Repeat with remaining glasses and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To make vanilla bean paste: place 6-10 whole vanilla bean pods into mixing bowl and grind <strong><b>20 sec\/speed 10<b><\/strong> or until pulverized. Add 3 tbsp pure vanilla extract and 2 tsp xanthan gum (optional) and stir <strong><b>3 sec\/speed 3<b><\/strong>. Transfer into a glass jar and use as required.","Vanilla bean paste can be replaced with vanilla extract.","Ensure mixing bowl, lid and butterfly whisk are thoroughly clean and dry before whipping eggs. Any residual grease or moisture will prevent eggs from properly aerating."],"basicInfo":["easy","5m","30m","20 glasses"]}